  "notes": "All per-hole data taken verbatim from the RFEG club page (rated recorridos 'FINCA ALGORFA - La Finca'), which lists Hdcp, Par and Metros per hole for every tee; per-hole meters and pars cross-check exactly with mScorecard and Hole19 (Azules card), and totals/ratings cross-check with Golfshake. Stroke index (Hdcp) is identical for all tees and both genders per RFEG: front 9 odd numbers, back 9 even (out 37 / in 35). Nine-hole totals: Blancas 3383/3011, Amarillas 3195/2837, Azules 3043/2694, Rojas 2888/2523, Naranjas 2553/2188 — each sums exactly to the tee total. Blancas and Amarillas are rated for men only. Naranjas tees are orange on the card; 'gold' used as nearest allowed color. Discrepancy: golfingholiday.com shows an older/incorrect card with hole 9 as par 4 and hole 18 as par 5 plus a different SI allocation; RFEG, mScorecard and Hole19 all agree on the card returned here. RFEG also lists a 'PROVISIONAL H2 Y H11' variant (temporary layout for holes 2 and 11) which was excluded as it is not the standard course. Note: golfify.io and hole19golf.com/courses/la-finca-golf contain data for a different course (La Finca Golf, Pozuelo de Alarcon, Madrid) and were disregarded."
